<title>KA ZUMHMI KA HNGALH CH185</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian nih zei ca velngeihnak a ka pek ka hngal lo, Dawtnak in zeica
 tlanh tlak lo, A ka tlanh ka hngal lo.

[C1]
   Sihmansehlaw, ka zumhmi ka hngalh, Ka Pathian sinah ka chiahmi
   vialte, Khi ni tiang a huhphenh khawh lai, Cu-caah ka ningzak lo.

[V2]
 Zeitin khamh hmuhnak zumhnak hi a ka pek ka hngal lo, Ka lungchung ah
 A-mah bia nih, Daihnak a ka pek zong.

[C2]
   Sihmansehlaw, ka zumhmi ka hngalh, Ka Pathian sinah ka chiahmi
   vialte, Khi ni tiang a huhphenh khawh lai, Cu-caah ka ningzak lo.

[V3]
 Zeitin Thlarau nih misual lung a thlen hi ka hngal lo, Baibal in Jesuh
 kong a thanh, Zumhnak lung a kan pek.

[C3]
   Sihmansehlaw, ka zumhmi ka hngalh, Ka Pathian sinah ka chiahmi
   vialte, Khi ni tiang a huhphenh khawh lai, Cu-caah ka ningzak lo.

[V4]
 Zeitik ka Bawi rat lai hngalh lo, Zan ah maw chun ceu ah, Nelrawn ah
 maw kan kal ti lai, Van ah dah kan ton lai?.

[C4]
   Sihmansehlaw, ka zumhmi ka hngalh, Ka Pathian sinah ka chiahmi
   vialte, Khi ni tiang a huhphenh khawh lai, Cu-caah ka ningzak lo.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
</song>